<h2><b>Position Analysis of Four Bar Mechanism (Grashof) - expT PROCEDURE</b></h2></br>
<h3>Objective:</h3></br>
<p style="padding-left:50px;">
To completely determine the position of four bar linkage given and thereby find out <img src="../images/exp3/Jg8DHTUJ.png" style="width:27px;height:30px ; position: relative; bottom: -15px; " >  and <img src="../images/exp3/LXINO81p.png" style="width:15px;height:28px ; position: relative; bottom: -5px; " > </br>
(transmission angle).</br></br></p>


<h3>PROCEDURE:</h3></br>

<p style="padding-left:50px;">
1. Read the values of link lengths under variables.</br></br>
2. Read the value of <img src="../images/exp1/nW11hRdS.png" style="width:27px;height:30px ; position: relative; bottom: -15px; " >  under variables</br></br>
3. Calculate the value of <img src="../images/exp1/YEQXbFAA.png" style="width:27px;height:30px ; position: relative; bottom: -15px; " > and <img src="../images/exp3/Jg8DHTUJ.png" style="width:27px;height:30px ; position: relative; bottom: -15px; " >.</br></br>
</p>



